			<td valign="Top">
	<h1><a name='Intro'>Web Applications</a></h1>
	<p>


	<span style="display:inline-block;">


		<span style="color:#000000;">The new ASP.NET technologies included in the Microsoft .NET Framework enable you to build complete Web applications from within Visual Studio .NET. On this page, find links to articles and other resources for building Web applications using ASP.NET.
		</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;


	</span>
	<p />
	</p>
	

<hr />

